data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This charming 4 bed, 2 bath house comes with a top-notch SimpliSafe security system including a front door camera, garage camera, and window sensors. Inside, you'll find a cozy living room with a wood-burning fireplace, a den perfect for relaxing, and a spacious kitchen with a dining area. The mudroom offers convenience and organization. The primary bedroom is generously sized with space for an office and includes a full bathroom with a walk-in closet. The garage in the basement provides ample storage space and parking. Enjoy outdoor living on the back deck that overlooks the partially fenced back and side yard. With a circular drive in front of the house, convenience is at your doorstep. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity!
